==Abstract==
[http://www.friendsofthedunes.org/ Friends of the Dunes], the client, teamed up with [http://www.humboldt.edu/ Humboldt State University's] Engineering introduction to design class to design and construct various aspects of the [http://www.friendsofthedunes.org/HCNC/ Humboldt Coastal Nature Center] (HCNC). Team Little Blue Dune Buggy was formed to design and implement trail lighting from the parking lot to specific events hosted at the HCNC. Little Blue Dune Buggy consists of [http://www.appropedia.org/User:Kyle.Sipes Kyle Sipes], [http://www.appropedia.org/User:Kdp18 Kyle Page], [http://www.appropedia.org/User:Lgm10 Laythen Martines], and [http://www.appropedia.org/User:Cb122 Curtis Beaudry]. Many brainstorming sessions resulted in several alternative solutions for the trail lighting. Each of these solutions were compared and scored according to how well they met specified criteria. The final solution was chosen through this process and several discussions with the client. The implemented solution consists of an on site solar powered light charging station.

